    • addCustomChunk

      public static void addCustomChunk(String name, SaveFileReader.CustomChunk chunk)
      Registers a custom save chunk reader/writer by name. This is mostly used for mods that need to save extra data.
      Parameters:
      name - a mod-specific, unique name for identifying this chunk. Prefixing is recommended.
